If you have any problems, please contact us at support@baseussecurity.com.

Baseus security offers the most comprehensive voice-controlled smart home experience with Alexa. Control your security devices hands-free. Just say it, Baseus security will obey.

Here’s a step by step guide:
(1). Download our "baseus Security" app in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2). Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you’re already registered);
(3). Turn on Baseus security equipment and connect them with “baseus Security” app;
(4). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect Echo with "Alexa" app;
(5). Search the Alexa Skills directory for "baseus Security";
(6). Click Enable skill of "baseus Security", then input your account username, password on the linking page;
(7). Talk to Echo "“Alexa,discover devices.”. Wait till Echo says "Discover is completed";
(8). Now all setup is done. Try talk to Echo to control your devices.

Here are the voice commands Baseus security has:

Camera
Alexa, turn on the camera
Alexa, turn off the camera
